1967;;The Taming of the Shrew;;American;;Franco Zeffirelli;;Elizabeth Taylor, Richard Burton;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Taming_of_the_Shrew_(1967_film);;Baptista Minola is attempting to marry off his two daughters; however, he will marry off his youngest, Bianca only if someone will marry his eldest, Katharina. Katharina is an ill-tempered shrewish woman but a lusty young nobleman, Petruchio, takes on the challenge of taming and marrying her. A subplot involves the wooing of Bianca by several suitors including handsome Lucentio, foppish Hortensio, and elderly Gremio.